249
00:13:48,584 --> 00:13:51,886
So it allows us to have this very fluid,

250
00:13:51,946 --> 00:13:56,009
very first-person, very subjective role-playing experience

251
00:13:56,490 --> 00:13:59,772
while still maintaining this objective

252
00:14:00,833 --> 00:14:02,034
point of view in the story.

253
00:14:03,895 --> 00:14:05,116
So what is the agreement we made?

254
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:12,665
