00:15:26,790 --> 00:15:29,871
and the fact that we didn't have the black bars,

281
00:15:30,591 --> 00:15:31,452
the letter boxing.

282
00:15:31,892 --> 00:15:32,733
to put words in.

283
00:15:32,813 --> 00:15:35,093
So we needed something that was very slick and very intuitive.

284
00:15:35,593 --> 00:15:39,615
And also, now that we moved to this different model,

285
00:15:39,735 --> 00:15:42,076
now that we're objective to the experience,

286
00:15:42,556 --> 00:15:45,057
we didn't have to write out the whole response anymore.

287
00:15:46,197 --> 00:15:47,958
So we came up with a slick little interface,

